Build-Depends: beancount, debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3, python3-beancount, python3-bs4, python3-chardet, python3-click, python3-lxml, python3-magic, python3-petl, python3-pytest <!nocheck>
Description: Importers Framework for Beancount Beangulp provides a framework for importing transactions into a Beancount ledger from account statements and other documents and for managing documents. . Beangulp is compatible with both Beancount 2.3 and the Beancount 3.0. Beangulp is the evolution of beancount.ingest in Beancount 2.3 and replaces it in the Beancount 3.0 release.
